result.name: Black Sugar Coffee & Lifestyle

reviews.text: Having breakfast at my favourite coffee shop. They have a very nice casual meeting and discussion area too!

I was pleasantly surprised by the oat flat white.  Oat turned out to be really better than soy.  The avocado and scrambled eggs on toast was outstanding too!  Food and coffee of this quality is a rare find in HK!  Highly recommended!

Front door facing the Mody road. 
I had a visit on weekend which I hvnt needed to wait for seats.
It is self-service so they would give menus to you and find a seat yourselves, then made orders on counter and pay.
Ample space around 5-6 small tables for 2 and 1 large table inside (with power socket). 
As their owner is a dog (shiba) lover, there are some shiba decoration, magazines and some souvenirs for sale. 

We ordered a cup of cappuccino, hand drip and also a pesto chicken pasta. The coffee were good and rich in aroma. The pasta was also fine but can improve a bit.

Overall, highly recommend if you want to find a cafe without many people in TST.

Such a cute place! These staff really know what they are doing. Lots of beans to choose from and they will happily make suggestions if you can't decide. Super cool decor, and cruisy music. Keep up the great work, team 😄 Wish I could come every day but I'm just visiting Hong Kong!
Staff is nice, can get busy in the late afternoon. Sometimes the dog is here... really cute guest!

reviews.text: 舊年年尾於帝國中心的好彩海鮮酒家，壽宴3圍，龍蝦烏冬底龍蝦未熟！最尾幾道菜放涼了！雞開始是凍的！伊麵炒飯都是凍的！連主角壽桃包都是凍的！ 一問之下原來廚房佬一早收曬工！
有兩大全層酒楼，可欣賞落地玻璃全海景，價格合理，惟御皇宴某經理怠客，周日飲早午茶容易揾位，但車埸小泊車請早！
這座位於尖沙咀東部的商業大廈，有中式酒樓，韓式餐館，美式咖啡店，商舖和便利店，更有一間基督教會在地庫。
商場内的 Starbucks 附設的坐位，感覺最優閒舒適。
Elite restaurants, dinner at namo. 5 stars because the bathrooms are beyond amazing! Automatic doors!! I will visit again when im back.

reviews.text:
2019.06.21

Black Sugar Coffee - TST East

Espresso

果酸強烈，但過後喉頭留下一抹清涼。

HAILE GEBRE - ETHIOPIA by Gardelli Specialty Coffees

“有什麼特別的？”
“這支昨天變了無花果味，不知今天如何。”
“好~就這支。”

乾粉味不突出。

“今天變回 Earl Grey。” 咖啡師試喝後認定。

我會說是伯爵茶加青檸檬：“伯檸茶”。
輕輕的檸酸，
茶味薄薄，
不俗，但我喝過更“檸茶”的精品咖啡。

比旺角分店大，
Starbucks 盤踞商場另一邊，
近距離接戰，
黑糖一點不輸。
